<book>
    <appendix id="foss4g_systems">
        <title>Free and Open Source Software for Geospatial Information
            Systems</title>
        
        <para>A range of related software packages can be used
            in addition to GeoNetwork opensource to deploy a full Spatial Data
            Infrastructure. These include Web Map Server software, GIS desktop
            applications and Web Map Viewers.</para>
        
        <para>Below you will find some examples of open source software available
        for each categories.</para>
        
        <section>
            <title>Web Map Server software</title>
            <itemizedlist>
                <listitem><para>GeoServer (All)<footnote id="os_support"><para>All = Windows, Linux and Mac OS X</para></footnote> <ulink url="http://www.geoserver.org"/></para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>MapServer (All) <ulink url="http://www.osgeo.org/mapserver"/></para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>MapGuide Open Source (Windows &amp; Linux) <ulink url="http://www.osgeo.org/mapguide"/></para></listitem>
            </itemizedlist>
        </section>

        <section>
            <title>GIS Desktop software</title>
            <itemizedlist>
                <listitem><para>GRASS (All) <ulink url="http://www.osgeo.org/grass"/></para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>gvSIG (All) <ulink url="http://www.gvsig.gva.es/"/></para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>uDig (All) <ulink url="http://udig.refractions.net"/></para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>Quantum GIS (All) <ulink url="http://www.osgeo.org/qgis"/></para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>OSSIM (Windows &amp; OSX) <ulink url="http://www.osgeo.org/ossim"/></para></listitem>
            </itemizedlist>
        </section>        

        <section>
            <title>Web Map Viewers</title>
            <itemizedlist>
                <listitem><para>OpenLayers (All) <ulink url="http://www.osgeo.org/openlayers"/></para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>MapBender (All) <ulink url="http://www.osgeo.org/mapbender"/></para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>MapBuilder (All) <ulink url="http://www.osgeo.org/mapbuilder"/></para></listitem>
            </itemizedlist>
        </section>
    </appendix>
